public final Connection getConnection()
                               throws SQLException
Returns a newly-allocated Connection by invoking either the DriverManager.getConnection(String) or the getConnection(String, String) method, depending on whether a non-null username was supplied to this DriverManagerDataSource's constructor.

This method never returns null.
